    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about maintenance, so it's spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for its next big adventure. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you're going to love it! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
