    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or swirls, protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains that fresh, new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creases or wear. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a documented service history, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014smooth, powerful, and silent. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
